{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"direction","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>CSS 属性 <strong><code>direction</code></strong> 用来设置文本、表列水平溢出的方向。 <code>rtl</code> 表示从右到左 (类似希伯来语或阿拉伯语)， <code>ltr</code> 表示从左到右 (类似英语等大部分语言).<iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/direction.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n<p>值得注意的是文本方向通常由文档定义 (e.g., with <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/dir\">HTML's <code>dir</code> attribute</a>) 而不是通过直接使用 <code>direction</code> 属性定义。</p>\n<p>该属性设置可以设置块级元素文本的基本方向，也可以设置由通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a>属性创建的嵌入元素的方向。与此同时，它还可以设置文本、块级元素的默认对齐方式，以及表行中的单元格的流动方向。</p>\n<p>与 HTML 中的 <code>dir</code> 属性不同，<code>direction</code>属性不会从表列继承到表单元格，因为 CSS 继承遵从文档流，而表单元格位于行内部，但不在列内部。</p>\n<p><code>direction</code> 属性和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a> 属性不受 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/all\"><code>all</code></a> 属性影响。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Keyword values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ltr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> rtl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"取值","title":"取值","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"ltr\"><code>ltr</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>默认属性。可设置文本和其他元素的默认方向是从左到右。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"rtl\"><code>rtl</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>可设置文本和其他元素的默认方向是从右到左。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"标准语法","title":"标准语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">ltr <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rtl</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">blockquote</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> rtl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-writing-modes/#direction","title":"CSS Writing Modes Level 4"}],"query":"css.properties.direction"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">初始值</a></th><td><code>ltr</code></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">适用元素</th><td>all elements</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">是否是继承属性</a></th><td>yes</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">计算值</a></th><td>as specified</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>discrete</td></tr></tbody></table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.direction","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode\"><code>writing-mode</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"CSS 属性 direction 用来设置文本、表列水平溢出的方向。 rtl 表示从右到左 (类似希伯来语或阿拉伯语)， ltr 表示从左到右 (类似英语等大部分语言).","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"direction","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"direction","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"direction","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"direction","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"direction","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/direction","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/direction/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS（层叠样式表）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction","title":"direction"}],"pageTitle":"direction - CSS（层叠样式表） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}